data.title: Red Bull Phenom: Alec Majerus
data.description:
Recently, Volcom's Wild In The Parks tour was approached by Red Bull to select one of its 15-19 year-old competitors to skate in the Red Bull Phenom contest at the 2013 X Games in Los Angeles. Coming straight off a winning effort at 3rd Lair Skatepark Sunday 21, 2013, Alec Majeras has been selected as our tour representative. Good luck to Alec as he represents all of our WITP skaters in LA at the Red Bull Phenom.

Alec's Info:

Birth Date: 5/31/1995 

Place of Birth: Rochester, MN 

Currently Living: Rochester, MN 

Stance: Goofy

data.title: Paul Cesar Distinguin Between Salvador and Tahiti
data.description:
Paul Cesar "PC" Distinguin is now focused on the Euro Pro Junior season, and he will try to get his qualification for the World Champs this week in Galicia at the last junior contest of the year. 
Here is his last clip filmed between Tahiti and Salvador showing why PC should be at the Junior World Champs in Brazil! 
GO PC! 

-Music-
Artist: Hot Lunch
Song: "Handy Denny"
Release: Hot Lunch
